snippet.title: Need For Speed: The Run - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
From the Golden Gate to the Empire State — Compete in The Run, an illicit race across the most iconic and treacherous roads from San Francisco to New York.

There are no rules and no allies in the cities, deserts, mountains and canyons that stand between you and the finish line.

In Need for Speed The Run, you'll weave through dense urban centers, rocket down icy mountain passes and navigate narrow canyons at breakneck speeds, all the while evading a relentless police force prepared -- and willing -- to use lethal force to take you down.
